# Frontend View Redesign — Steam Deck-Style UI

Complete rewrite of [LibraryFrontendPane.kt](file:///home/max/Build/GNP/Game/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/library/components/LibraryFrontendPane.kt) for a polished, controller-first, Steam Deck-inspired experience.

## Design Goals
- **Hero spotlight** — Full-screen background art of focused game with gradient overlay, game title, source badge, and Play button
- **Horizontal game carousel** at bottom — smooth scrolling, clear focus ring, controller D-pad navigation
- **Frosted glass top tab bar** — "L1 < LIBRARY · STORE · DOWNLOADS > R1" with subtle backdrop blur
- **AIO Store toggle** — When `aioStoreMode=true`, single "Store" tab shows all sources; when `false`, separate Steam/Epic/GOG/Amazon tabs
- **Controller-first** — Every element focusable via D-pad, L1/R1 tab switching, A to select, B to go back
- **Clean empty states** — For tabs with no content (Downloads, empty stores)
- **No loading spinner stuck** — Pagination already fixed, just render skeleton placeholders during load

## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] [LibraryFrontendPane.kt](file:///home/max/Build/GNP/Game/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/library/components/LibraryFrontendPane.kt)

**Full rewrite** with the following structure:

1. **[LibraryFrontendPane](file:///home/max/Build/GNP/Game/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/library/components/LibraryFrontendPane.kt#68-184)** — Root composable
   - Dark background, L1/R1 tab switching, passes state to child views
   - Tab bar overlaid at top with L1/R1 hint icons

2. **`FrontendTopBar`** — Frosted glass tab bar
   - Semi-transparent background with `surfaceColorAtElevation`
   - L1/R1 icons flanking tabs
   - Selected tab has bold text + accent underline
   - Unselected tabs are dimmed
   - Animated selection indicator

3. **`FrontendLibraryView`** — Hero + carousel (LIBRARY tab)
   - Full-bleed hero artwork of focused game with gradient scrim
   - Game title (large, bold, white, drop shadow)
   - Game source badge (Steam/Epic/GOG/Amazon/Custom icon)
   - Play button with accent color, rounded corners, icon + text
   - `LazyRow` game carousel at bottom with 16:9 aspect ratio cards
   - Focus ring glow on selected card + slight scale-up
   - Pagination via `snapshotFlow` observer

4. **`FrontendStoreView`** — Grid for store tabs
   - When AIO enabled: shows all games
   - When AIO disabled: filters by [GameSource](file:///home/max/Build/GNP/Game/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/library/components/LibraryAppItem.kt#140-150)
   - `LazyVerticalGrid` with 4 columns, hero aspect ratio cards
   - Focus ring + scale animation on cards
   - Pagination support

5. **`FrontendDownloadsView`** — Placeholder
   - Large icon, "No Active Downloads" text, dimmed

6. **[findSteamGridDBImage](file:///home/max/Build/GNP/Game/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/library/components/LibraryFrontendPane.kt#528-544)** — Keep existing helper unchanged

